</style></head><body class="pdf ko-KR" lang="ko-KR"><article id="2ef214c9-48c3-80cf-9853-ebef1ed947c9" class="page sans"><header><h1 class="page-title" dir="auto">v2 API 명세서</h1><p class="page-description" dir="auto"></p></header><div class="page-body"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2ef214c9-48c3-80f8-bf25-d8de03529b6d"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="2f0214c9-48c3-8041-8d7d-ec9156f4e5c5" class=""><code>/api/v2/auth</code> 하위 API들만 인증 없이 접근 가능</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2ef214c9-48c3-80d9-a572-ef7abcb933df" class="">유저 API</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2f0214c9-48c3-8086-ba10-c07e051363d2"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2f0214c9-48c3-809c-9878-e97b6ae639a7" class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>[POST] /api/v2/users - 유저 추가 * </summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="2f0214c9-48c3-808a-9d23-f02eddd9671d" class="block-color-teal_background">유저를 추가하는 API<br/>기본 유저(admin)은 기본적으로 존재함</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-8042-87b9-c13ce1111526" class="">
