shareId: 삭제할 공유 링크 ID</code></pre></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-801c-af87-d4abb632a147" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-80eb-add4-eb694c51118c" class=""><strong>Response Body</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-8092-a4d4-f38c2c650d39" class=""><code>Status: 204</code></p></div></details></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-80c1-bdb9-fcd5ccb880ba" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2f0214c9-48c3-805f-8ad9-ef504615f737" class="">시스템 API</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2f0214c9-48c3-80d9-88e4-eb28e462a8ec"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2f0214c9-48c3-808d-9e14-cfe125bb2b0b" class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>[GET] /api/v2/system/status - 시스템 상태 조회</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="2f0214c9-48c3-800c-abc2-e2a68fe4e0b7" class="block-color-teal_background">시스템 정보 조회하는 API</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-8058-afa2-fbb423ebee72" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-800f-a996-ca63956597e1" class=""><strong>Response Body</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-803e-a31d-dd93698f097f" class=""><code>Status: 200</code></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><pre id="2f0214c9-48c3-80bb-a8b4-de3c92f38c6f" class="code code-wrap"><code class="language-json" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">{
    &quot;diskFree&quot; : Long //남은 용량 (바이트)
}</code></pre></div></details></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2f0214c9-48c3-80f3-a053-c57aadecc4bb" class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>[GET] /api/v2/system/health - DB 연결 상태 등 가용성 조회</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="2f0214c9-48c3-80fa-926e-eab88cc12200" class="block-color-teal_background">시스템 가용성 조회하는 API</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-806a-8f64-c970a9261538" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-8098-ad23-e764fd2cb3a8" class=""><strong>Response Body</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2f0214c9-48c3-8041-b5df-f6d2489f63ca" class=""><code>Status: 200</code></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><pre id="2f0214c9-48c3-8044-8050-d2cfb244bae2" class="code code-wrap"><code class="language-json" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">{
    &quot;status&quot; : &quot;good&quot;
}</code></pre></div></details></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="380214c9-48c3-8070-a8ed-de9c71eb1bac" class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>[GET] /api/v2/transcoding/settings - 트랜스코딩 설정 조회 *</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="380214c9-48c3-80bd-8f99-f144128c288e" class="block-color-teal_background">현재 설정된 트랜스코딩 설정 조회</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="380214c9-48c3-8096-93d4-cb3d1b936a69" class="">
